text: Objective, Burma! is a 1945 American World War II action movie directed by Raoul Walsh and starring Errol Flynn, James Brown, William Prince, George Tobias, Henry Hull, Warner Anderson. It was distributed by Warner Bros. and was nominated for three Academy Awards in 1946. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1945 war movies Category:1940s action movies Category:American action movies Category:World War II movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by Raoul Walsh Category:Movies set in Myanmar
